TiddlyRecon
TiddlyWeb data explorer

Configuration

The host URI is defined in scripts/config.js.

Dependencies

TiddlyRecon requires both jQuery and chrjs:
    http://jquery.com
    http://github.com/tiddlyweb/chrjs
    http://code.google.com/p/jquery-json/ (for chrjs)
The bld/init.sh script automatically downloads these external dependencies.

In addition, YUICompressor is used for minification (optional):
    http://yuilibrary.com/projects/yuicompressor
